description: Assigns the DELETED status to an Evaluation, rendering it unusable. After invoking the DeleteEvaluation operation, you can use the GetEvaluation operation to verify that the status of the Evaluation changed to DELETED. Caution: The results of the DeleteEvaluation operation are irreversible.

parameters.name: EvaluationId
parameters.description: A user-supplied ID that uniquely identifies the Evaluation to delete.

nested_items.name: EvaluationId
nested_items.description: A user-supplied ID that uniquely identifies the Evaluation. This value should be identical to the value of the EvaluationId in the request.
